oji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係識一個朋友會企係到食 仲要係佢自己講行住食會影響到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前成功令佢介左一排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但唔知佢會唔會頂唔到又食番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6e9796c7f070a79c0285c9044bc9287b691cd","tid":154263,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"觀塘好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85f61640bc15bb933a24d85fdd2b9b04ec6059a","tid":154263,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"好撚同意"},{"pid":"4bf3c69e08d8ffee9cd71a606188175c1f5e24d3","tid":154263,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"有一個仆街負評"},{"pid":"9250d8df90e4ab1cd3e71b4df6d08555a21a18e7","tid":154263,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"b51bda65d08a785f9162b65757929240f1d1e70c","tid":154263,"uid":69877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"行住食真係仆街<br />\n<br />\n利申：煙剷"},{"pid":"87c4b939a8a175305a6878f8e4474365a0d4121d","tid":154263,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>犯法呀？立左再講啦小朋友</blockquote><br />\n咁祝你肺癌死囉，點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講唔掂就咒人？<br />\n小朋友到你吖"},{"pid":"d457b1eba618ba15994d1499527c54b838c1558f","tid":154263,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>犯